Package edu.monash.fit2099.interfaces

Interface ActionInterface

All Known Implementing Classes:
Action, AttackAction, AttackStegosaurBehaviour, DoNothingAction, DrinkAction, DropItemAction, EatBehaviour, EatPterodactyl, FeedDinoAction, GettingMatedDoNothing, KickAction, LayEggAction, MateBehaviour, MoveActorAction, PickFruitFromPlantAction, PickUpItemAction, Player.SleepAction, PurchaseAction, QuitAction, SpitBehaviour, WindowSmashAction
public interface ActionInterface
This interface provides the ability to add methods to Action, without modifying code in the engine, or downcasting references in the game.
